CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 11, 1950, pg. 11, reads: "Recently Married - Mr. and Mrs. Taulton McCullough are among the city's recent newlyweds.  The couple was married on Feb. 25.  The bride is the former Miss Louise Farrish. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Women and men, including Joanna Farrish Hooper seated second from left, Addie Farrish Crawford second from right, Evelyn Farrish Terry on right, Veola Farrish Moon standing seventh from right, Richard Terry fifth, Clyde T. Crawford fourth, and Arnold Moon second from right, gathered around groom Taulton McCullough and bride Louise Farrish McCullough, behind table with two tiered wedding cake
